# Confirm Session Availability Modals

This section contains modals for tutors to confirm their session availability.

## Modal Types

- **Availability Confirmation**: Modals for tutors to confirm or decline session availability
- **Recurring Session Options**: Options for confirming availability for recurring sessions
- **Time Slot Selection**: Modals for selecting preferred time slots

## Design Guidelines

- Use semantic spacing tokens (modal, section, element)
- Use design system Button components (Available/Unavailable from CTA Tutors Button)
- Follow consistent modal layout patterns with other pre-session modals
- Include proper header, content, and button sections
- Use appropriate color tokens for availability states

## Component Reuse

- `AvailableButton` and `UnavailableButton` from CTA Tutors Button element
- Standard modal layout patterns from Edit Session/Delete Session modals
- Design system Alert components for availability status messages
